data.description: Welcome to this wonderful townhome in the highly sought after Audubon community.  Just a little TLC is needed to make this home your own.  Spacious, beautiful, and bright, this home is ready for its new owner.   The first floor boasts a powder room, spacious kitchen with large pantry, dining room and large great room with vaulted ceilings and fireplace. Sliders open to private back deck. Upstairs, the second floor offers the large master bedroom with oversized windows and double closets. There is also a loft with double closets and windows that overlook the living room.  This space can easily be finished off to provide a second bedroom or used as office space. As if all of this wasn't enough, the  finished lower level provides additional living space with large slider doors. Large storage closets and separate laundry area with even more storage. All this plus a reserved carport, one parking spot and plenty of overflow parking.  Don't miss this great opportunity to live in the award winning West Chester Area school district; the central location also makes getting to the shops and restaurants in West Chester Boro a breeze.
